--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7560397b5d3378a468a5f05601876426, type: 3}
  m_Name: Zone 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Dialoue.DialogueData
  backgroundArt: {fileID: 2800000, guid: 9116669d9ab2a4f4d85079042272ec6c, type: 3}
  lines:
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 90112a895fec9364f804c5cb0ebc31d6, type: 2}
    text: "When I was your age, my house was far away from my school, you know\u2026 "
    eventIDs: []
    onLineComplete:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 90112a895fec9364f804c5cb0ebc31d6, type: 2}
    text: "I had to do long hours of walk to get there, I had to go by myself. No
      bus, no cars to help me get there. I\u2019d wake up at 5 in the morning; can
      you believe that!! "
    eventIDs: []
    onLineComplete:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 90112a895fec9364f804c5cb0ebc31d6, type: 2}
    text: 'So, I needed great shoes, I was going through a lot, sometimes even climbing
      rocky paths, or scary places.  '
    eventIDs: []
    onLineComplete:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 90112a895fec9364f804c5cb0ebc31d6, type: 2}
    text: "And don\u2019t get me started on the weather; sunny, cloudy, rain or even
      snow, I HAD TO GO BY FOOT.  "
    eventIDs: []
    onLineComplete:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 20ca1bf72c3f96c46869890db2259f25, type: 2}
    text: "Aren\u2019t you a bit dramatic, grandpa...?"
    eventIDs: []
    onLineComplete:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 90112a895fec9364f804c5cb0ebc31d6, type: 2}
    text: "Dramatic? Me? Non-sense, get me another drink\u2026 "
    eventIDs:
    - Zone1_Finished
    onLineComplete:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
